data.description: Elegant Modern Home in Narcoossee Village - Ideal Blend of Luxury and Convenience  Discover the epitome of contemporary living in this stunning single-family home nestled within the coveted community of Narcoossee Village, mere minutes away from the allure of Lake Nona and Medical City. Built in 2016, this remarkable residence presents an exceptional opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort, style, and convenience.  Property Features:  4 Bedrooms, 3/1 Baths: This exquisite home boasts a thoughtfully designed layout featuring four spacious bedrooms and three-and-a-half baths, catering to the needs of both residents and guests.  Master Bedroom on First Floor: A luxurious master suite on the main level offers unparalleled privacy and convenience, creating an oasis of relaxation within your own home.  Bonus Room for Versatility: Enhance your living experience with a versatile bonus room, ideal for a home office, entertainment space, or even a tranquil reading nook.  Dual Family Rooms: Enjoy the luxury of two distinct family rooms, one on each level, allowing for a seamless flow of entertainment and relaxation.  Gourmet Kitchen: The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a culinary enthusiast's dream. Adorned with stainless-steel appliances and granite countertops, this space effortlessly blends functionality and elegance.  Open Concept Design: The spacious open floor plan exudes modern appeal, fostering a sense of unity and connection throughout the main living areas.  2-Car Garage & Paved Driveway: Accommodate your vehicles with ease, courtesy of a two-car garage and a beautifully paved driveway.  Prime Location:  Located in close proximity to the Orlando Airport, Lake Nona, East Lake Toho, and Lakefront Beach/Park, this residence offers an unparalleled advantage in terms of accessibility and recreation. The nearby boat launch and walking trails provide opportunities for outdoor enthusiasts to revel in the natural beauty that surrounds the area.  Community Amenities:  Narcoossee Village presents a dynamic community environment, featuring a refreshing pool and an inviting playground. These amenities offer both relaxation and recreation, creating an atmosphere of balance and enjoyment.  Local Charm and Convenience:  Embrace the convenience of living centrally to shopping centers, renowned restaurants, and major highways. Local favorite Crabby Bills adds a touch of charm to the dining experience, further enhancing the lifestyle that this community offers.  This exquisite single-family home in Narcoossee Village stands as a testament to modern luxury, providing a harmonious blend of sophistication, comfort, and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this remarkable property your own. Schedule a showing today and witness firsthand the allure of this masterfully crafted residence.
